sequenceDiagram
    participant A as Agent
    participant G as API Gateway
    participant SvcRoutes as service-routes
    participant PG as PostgreSQL
    participant Algo as Optimization Engine

    Note over A,SvcRoutes: Agent creates a new tournee

    A->>G: POST /api/routes/tournees<br/>{date, id_zone, id_agent}
    G->>SvcRoutes: Forward request
    
    SvcRoutes->>PG: Get containers in zone
    PG-->>SvcRoutes: 45 containers to collect
    
    SvcRoutes->>Algo: Optimize route
    Note over Algo: 1. Filter by fill level > 70%<br/>2. Apply 2-opt algorithm<br/>3. Calculate ETA
    
    Algo-->>SvcRoutes: Optimized route<br/>{order: [c1,c5,c3,c2...], distance: 12.5km, duration: 45min}
    
    SvcRoutes->>PG: Save tournee
    PG-->>SvcRoutes: Tournee saved
    
    SvcRoutes-->>G: Tournee created with steps
    G-->>A: 201 Created

    Note over A,SvcRoutes: Agent starts tournee

    A->>G: PATCH /api/routes/tournees/:id/statut<br/>{statut: "EN_COURS"}
    G->>SvcRoutes: Forward
    
    SvcRoutes->>PG: Update statut
    PG-->>SvcRoutes: OK
    
    SvcRoutes-->>G: 200 OK
    G-->>A: Tournee started

    Note over A,SvcRoutes: Agent completes container

    A->>G: POST /api/routes/tournees/:id/etapes<br/>{id_conteneur, heure_collecte}
    G->>SvcRoutes: Forward
    
    SvcRoutes->>PG: Record step + update container
    PG-->>SvcRoutes: Step saved
    
    SvcRoutes->>PG: Update tournee progress
    PG-->>SvcRoutes: Progress: 3/45
    
    SvcRoutes-->>G: Step recorded
    G-->>A: Progress updated

    Note over A,SvcRoutes: Agent ends tournee

    A->>G: PATCH /api/routes/tournees/:id/statut<br/>{statut: "TERMINEE", distance_reelle, duree_reelle}
    G->>SvcRoutes: Forward
    
    SvcRoutes->>PG: Save final stats
    PG-->>SvcRoutes: Tournee completed
    
    SvcRoutes-->>G: Tournee completed
    G-->>A: Stats: 45 collected, 12.8km, 52min